@{PAR}@{FG HIGHLIGHT}@{B}ColorToRGB@{UB}@{FG TEXT}@{LINE}
@{PAR}@{B}Separate a portable pixmap into three portable graymaps.@{UB}@{LINE}
@{PAR}Reads a portable pixmap as input. Writes three portable graymaps as output, one each for red, green, and blue.@{LINE}
@{PAR}See also @{" RGBToColor " LINK "rgb3toppm.guide/MAIN"}.@{LINE}
